THE FONT:

The No Man's Sky portal glyphs font, as I understand it, was created by Ghuyajil,
and released into the public domain.
https://nomanssky.gamepedia.com/UserProfile:Ghuyajil
Specifically, the file here was obtained from
https://nms.miraheze.org/wiki/File:NMS-Glyphs-Mono.ttf

